  <h2>3. Defining the menu</h2>

  <p>Each dropdown has a corresponding menu that gets hidden by default. The menu requires the following attribute to function <%= code 'data-dropdown-target="menu"' %>. The element the target is appended to also requires the class name <%= code " class='hidden'" %> to be present.</p>

<div class="not-prose mb-6">
<% content_for :html, flush: true do %>
<div data-controller="dropdown">
  <button data-action="dropdown#toggle click@window->dropdown#hide">Dropdown</button>
  <ul class="hidden" data-dropdown-target="menu">
    <li>Menu list item 1</li>
    <li>Menu list item 2</li>
  </ul>
</div>
<% end %>
<%= render_snippet %>
</div>
